description:
check-tempest-dsvm-cells-full failed with a ton of errors in this patch, but I don't think it's related to this patch:

check-tempest-dsvm-cells-full

Looking at the first error in the parent cell log here:

http://logs.openstack.org/59/72559/2/check/check-tempest-dsvm-cells-full/67d158b/logs/screen-n-cell-region.txt.gz?level=TRACE

Looks like some issue with messaging.  I don't know if this is a regression due to the recent oslo.messaging changes in nova or not.
title: check-tempest-dsvm-cells-full fails hard in check queue
